<mvt:item name="html_profile" />
<head><meta charset="utf-8"><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1"><base href="&mvte:global:basehref;"><title>Core Returns | Sinister Diesel</title><meta name="description" content="Prepare, package and return an eligible diesel component core and understand Sinister Diesel core-credit timing and conditions."><mvt:if expr="g.useDevResources EQ 1"><mvt:item name="head" param="css_list_dev" /><mvt:else><mvt:item name="head" param="css_list" /></mvt:if><mvt:item name="head" param="head_tag" /></head>
<body class="single-column sd2-policy-page"><mvt:item name="hdft" param="global_header" /><mvt:item name="hdft" param="header" />
<main class="sd2-cp sd2-policy sd2-core"><section class="sd2-policy__hero"><div class="sd2-cp__shell"><nav class="sd2-policy__breadcrumb" aria-label="Breadcrumb"><a href="&mvte:urls:SFNT:auto;">Home</a><span>/</span><span>Core returns</span></nav><p class="sd2-cp__eyebrow">Returns / Remanufacturing loop</p><h1>Send the core.<br>Keep parts moving.</h1><p>Prepare and package the reusable component correctly so inspection and eligible credit can move without preventable delays.</p><div class="sd2-cp__actions"><a class="sd2-cp__button sd2-cp__button--primary" href="/pdfs_forms/Core%20Return%20Form.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Download the form</a><a class="sd2-cp__button" href="help-returns-exchanges.html">Returns help</a></div></div></section>
	<div class="sd2-cp__signal"><div><span>01</span><strong>Drain and prepare</strong></div><div><span>02</span><strong>Protect and document</strong></div><div><span>03</span><strong>Ship and track</strong></div></div>
	<section class="sd2-cp__section"><div class="sd2-cp__shell sd2-policy__layout"><aside><p class="sd2-cp__label">Core-return path</p><h2>Condition and timing determine credit.</h2><p>Use the correct form, protect the component from shipping damage and retain the tracking number through refund processing.</p></aside><article class="sd2-policy__content"><mvt:item name="readytheme" param="contentsection( 'core-returns' )" /></article></div></section>
</main><mvt:item name="hdft" param="footer" /><mvt:item name="hdft" param="global_footer" /></body></html>
